            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic Candidilla infans iacet <lb n="2"/>quae non conpleto bimatu <lb n="3"/>percepit et sic in pace quievit <lb n="4"/>cui aeternam domum parentes <lb n="5"/>semper inviti fecerunt <lb n="6"/>deposita die XVII <expan><abbr>Kal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> Augustas <lb n="7"/>Anicio Basso et <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Filippo <expan><abbr>vv</abbr><ex>iris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cc</abbr><ex>larissimis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Tafel wurde als Standplatte für eine Statue wiederverwendet. (B): Mazzoleni, AE 1979: Z. 2: completo; AE 1979: Z. 4: donum; Mazzoleni, AE 1979: Z. 6: Aug(ustas).</p>
            </div>
